text: George William Vella, (born 24 April 1942) is a Maltese politician. He was the 10th President of Malta from 2019 to 2024. He was Malta's Minister for Foreign Affairs from 1996 to 1998 and from 2013 to 2017. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Malta
